sentences: Craig Dimech (born September 1970), known by his stage name Meck, is a British DJ who was the former head of free2air recordings and later Frenetic Recordings.
2009: "Windmills" (samples "The Windmills of Your Mind" by Dusty Springfield)
2010: "Feels Like a Prayer" (mashup of "Like a Prayer" by Madonna and "Feels Like Home")
